column2: this [This.GetName] is actually a rare artifact. \nDo not believe any rumor you hear
this [This.GetName] is a masterpiece of a dropout apprentice
this [This.GetName] is incomplete, although still fully usable
there is no interesting story behind this [This.GetName]
the angry spirit haunts anyone who dares to wear this [This.GetName]
this [This.GetName] was accidentally created by a drunk craftsman
the symbols and runes covering this [This.GetName] actually mean and do nothing
this [This.GetName] was reforged from another one, but it severely decreased the quality
this [This.GetName] was never deliberately enchanted, but acquired its magic by chance
this [This.GetName] was fished out of a lake
this [This.GetName] is an underwhelming replica of a legendary original
traces of the original owners blood can still be seen on this [This.GetName]
this [This.GetName] is designed after one worn by a famed hero
this [This.GetName] was stolen from a demon
this [This.GetName] matches the description of one worn by a hero in a popular children's lullaby
this [This.GetName] was found in the city's library along with other debris gathered in memory of an unknown conflict
this [This.GetName] has been tainted by some strange magic
the appearance of this [This.GetName] has been altered by someone to hide its identity
this [This.GetName] once was the a family heirloom of a fallen noble
this [This.GetName] supposed to be cursed, but for some reason became enchanted instead
this [This.GetName] was presented as a reward to the winner of a famous tournament in the distant past
this [This.GetName] initially supposed to be a mere replica, but accidentally surpassed the original
this [This.GetName] was crafted by an enigmatic individual who wanted to be remembered, but whose name was erased from history
this [This.GetName] has passed through much to attain its magical properties
the magical properties of a [This.GetName] such as this intrigue the mind. It was constructed from the finest parts of many different artifacts that were worn by many different heroes
originally fashioned for a ruler's burial, this [This.GetName] was instead entrusted to his successor, who began the tradition of passing it on to the worthiest champions of the realm
this [This.GetName] was found in the process of plundering the depths of an ancient tomb
a tyrant, who took enormous pride in his appearance, was wearing this [This.GetName] the day he was murdered by his own servants
the origins of this [This.GetName] are unknown
this [This.GetName] was the spark that ignited full-scale war between neighboring realms, as they vied to acquire it
this [This.GetName] is the only remaining proof of a mystic creature's existence, which died a long time ago
the original owner of this [This.GetName] spent the last years of his life traveling the world in search of esoteric secrets
sometimes this [This.GetName] glows with the essence of several lives that ended too soon
when you gaze too long at this [This.GetName], it also gazes back at you
this [This.GetName] whispers its original owners name from realms beyond
once upon a time a wise hermit has tried to understand the power of this [This.GetName], but has been driven mad by it
this [This.GetName] belongs to those who are dead. All who have worn it have died, and all who wear it yet shall follow
many a hero has wielded this [This.GetName] through many an age, and the tales sung of it can be heard from one end of the world to the other
this [This.GetName] was crafted with a technique millennia beyond its time. Few craftsmans have been able to replicate the quality
all who chance to behold this [This.GetName], desire it. Those who possess it must shed blood to keep it. And those who deem themselves above its allure are the most endangered by it
the very sight of this [This.GetName] was enough to settle disputes that would otherwise lead to war
this [This.GetName] has existed since before time began
this [This.GetName] holds the secret to existence for those who can decipher its intricate design
materials from what this [This.GetName] was crafted do not exist in this world
